    • CourseList

      public CourseList​(java.lang.String filename)
      CourseList constructor function that creates a course list from given file
      参数:
      filename - a filename directs to a proper documented txt file containing course information The given file is supposed to be documented, otherwise the sections created will not be viable. the file should be under the same directory as will the program is run

  • 方法详细资料

    • getClass

      public Section getClass​(int cnum)
      getClass is a getter that returns the section with given index
      参数:
      cnum - a index of the section the user want to obtain
      返回:
      the section with given index cnum is supposed to be within the range of sections list, otherwise this function will fail.

      返回:
